HEADWORD: off-site
<hw>off-site</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Taking place or located away from
the specified site; <as>as, an <ex>off-site</ex> waste treatment
operation</as>. Opposite to <ant>on-site</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
